activities: F5 Networks is the leading developer and provider of software-defined application services. Those services include maintenance and support services for its hardware and software products.  F5 may receive and process data from its business customers in order to provide its maintenance and support services, and this data may contain personal data.  F5’s Safe Harbor certification covers the personal data that F5 receives on behalf of its business customers in order to provide maintenance and support services to such customers related to F5’s signaling delivery controller products (the “Support Data”). F5 is a data processor for Support Data and will only process such data on behalf of and under the instructions of its customers.
